    <briefdescription>
<para>System that processes heading and rotation physics. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system updates the rotation state of entities based on their SteeringComponent. It calculates the target rotation from input, applies rotation speed and dampening, and updates the RotationStateComponent and DirectionComponent. </para>
